## Why This Is Asked
Tests ability to design multi-tenant inference systems with strict latency requirements, data isolation guarantees, and production-safe deployment strategies for TensorFlow Serving on Kubernetes.

## Key Concepts
- Multi-tenant request routing and isolation
- Per-tenant post-processing adapters
- Dynamic batching optimization per tenant
- Canary rollouts and versioned adapter management
